FeedPackage.Description: Dependency injection modules for SimpleInjector that can be used to integrate MvcSiteMapProvider into an existing dependency injection setup. You may customize this configuration to allow for replacement of virtually any part of MvcSiteMapProvider by implementing one of its interfaces and injecting an instance of your implementation. This package requires manual configuration to integrate with SimpleInjector, but is the least invasive option that won't bypass any existing DI bootstrapping code.
